ofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://7i.7iskusstv.com/y2020/nomer7/bpoljak/\">Boris Polyak. Memories.</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Mathematician#Ershov\" title=\"Mathematician\">Andrey Ershov</a>, <a href=\"/Mikhail_R._Shura-Bura\" title=\"Mikhail R. Shura-Bura\">Mikhail R. Shura-Bura</a> (<b>1980</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ershov.iis.nsk.su/archive/eaindex.asp?lang=2&amp;gid=910\">The Early Development of Programming in the USSR</a></i>. in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicholas_C._Metropolis\">Nicholas C. Metropolis</a> (ed.) <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=578384\">A History of Computing in the Twentieth Century</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Academic_Press\">Academic Press</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ershov.iis.nsk.su/archive/eaimage.asp?did=28792&amp;fileid=173671\">preprint pp. 44</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The date of 24.11.1968 in the video title seems wrong. As announced, the interview was taken a week after the end of the <a href=\"/Stanford-ITEP_Match\" title=\"Stanford-ITEP Match\">Stanford-ITEP Match</a> in 1967. A broadcast in November 1968 is further unlikely due to the famous <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9F%D0%B8%D1%81%D1%8C%D0%BC%D0%BE_%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%B2%D1%8F%D0%BD%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B0_%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%B2%D1%8F%D1%82%D0%B8\">letter</a> in support of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexander_Esenin-Volpin\">Esenin-Volpin</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p>